Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.43,0:26:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天！泳衣！危机！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.25,0:26:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,摇勒摇勒！咪咪！
